# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Pre-order traversal
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
0. Do the pre-order traversal.
1. Kepp collecting the node values in an array.
2. As soon as get the leaf child, push the current collection of nodes in the answer array.
3. At end just convert all the paths as per output requirement
4. Return you final collection of paths
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
$$O(n)$$
- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
